    },
    {
      "type": "accuracy",
      "location": "Intel’s Mesh Architecture",
      "issue": "Phrases like 'infamous for its multi-year delay' and 'made it all the way to stepping E5 before release' carry a highly critical tone regarding Intel's execution.",
      "suggestion": "Do not soften the critique. Use '因长达数年的延期而臭名昭著' and '直到修改至E5步进才最终发布' to capture the frustration."
    },
    {
      "type": "accuracy",
      "location": "Intel Xeon Coral Rapids",
      "issue": "Phrases like 'victim of Lip-Bu’s streamlining', 'dead', and 'treading water'.",
